title: Agro Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Western, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Coffee house and roaster. Offers vegan choices like muffin, brownie, or sweet bread; sandwich and wrap, soup, chili, and salad. Uses much as possible fair trade, local, organic, and non-GMO ingredients. Free Wi-Fi. Short walk from #50 drop off at Granville Island's entrance.
